New String Methods
isBlank()
strip()
stripLeading()
stripTrailing()
repeat(n)
3. Files API Enhancements.
....................................
Read String from File
import java.nio.file.*;

public class FileExample {

    public static void main(String[] args)
            throws Exception {

        String data =
            Files.readString(
                Path.of("test.txt"));

        System.out.println(data);
    }
}
Write String to File
Files.writeString(
        Path.of("test.txt"),
        "Hello Java 11");
Benefits

✔ Very simple file handling
✔ Less boilerplate code

